description:
&lt;p&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;Call Handler &lt;/span&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you want to join the NHS but didn’t think you had the necessary skills?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Well The Staffordshire Mental Health Access &amp; Helpline Team are offering a fantastic opportunity with flexible hours allowing you to develop a rewarding career within the NHS.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&lt;strong&gt;&lt;span style=&quot;text-decoration: underline;&quot;&gt;The Staffordshire Mental Health Access &amp; Helpline Team – “Putting service users at the heart of everything we do.”&lt;/span&gt;&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We are now adding to our fantastic multi-disciplinary team of enthusiastic, self-motivated, innovative, fabulously friendly and supportive individuals.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;The Staffordshire Mental Health Access &amp; Helpline Teamis the first point of contact for people requiring a mental health service.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;ul&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We receive all &lt;strong&gt;new referrals&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We contact those individuals &lt;strong&gt;by phone to identify their needs&lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;
&lt;p&gt;We receive calls to our &lt;strong&gt;helpline &lt;/strong&gt;&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;/ul&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Are you looking for flexible shift working covering days, nights and weekends?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you enjoy working with people?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you have an interest in mental health?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Do you have strong IT skills and a good telephone manner?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt; &lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Did you answer yes?&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Then please apply.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;It’s that simple.&lt;/p&gt;
